===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[accusative]] [[case]]}}

# {{grammar}}: [[case]] used to mark the immediate [[object]] ([[direct object]]) on which the action or influence of a [[transitive verb]] has its limited influence.
#: ''I see '''the car'''.''
#: ''I hear '''a bell'''.''
#: ''I watch '''television'''.''
#: ''I play '''football'''.''

